node.title: NFL legend Tom Brady reportedly retiring after record-breaking career
node.description: The 44-year-old is reportedly stepping away from the game after 22 seasons and seven Super Bowl victories.
node.content: ["Tampa Bay Buccaneers quarterback Tom Brady is reportedly set to retire from the NFL after 22 seasons and a record seven Super Bowl victories.", "American sports network ESPN has cited \"multiple sources\" as confirming the 44-year-old has played his final NFL game.", "Brady's Buccaneers were eliminated in the divisional round of the NFL playoffs by Los Angeles Rams on Monday.", "More to come", "\u00a0"]
